{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_03_02",
  "title": "fran 2話 ふたりで星見市へ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちは、{user}さん\n休日にわざわざありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ {user}-san.\nThank you for coming on your day off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、franさんこそ\n新曲のリリースやら何やらでお疲れでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚it's okay‚ fran-san.\nYou must be tired with the release of the new song and all too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "スケジュール通りに進めてますし、いつも通りですよ\nだらだら仕事したって効率悪いだけですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're proceeding as scheduled‚ so everything's normal.\nWorking aimlessly is just inefficient.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "で、ここが星見市なんですね\nなんて言うか、凄く……フツーなとこですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ this is Hoshimi City.\nIt's… quite ordinary here‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "実際、普通の地方都市ですしね。だから余計に\n最近までは、長瀬麻奈が名物みたいな感じが強くて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Indeed‚ it's just an ordinary provincial city. That's why\nMana Nagase was considered a local specialty until recently.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "はあ、名物ですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ a local specialty?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "この駅前でもデビュー前にチラシ配りをしたんですけど\n新人のチラシなんか誰も受け取ってくれなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even here at the station‚ she handed out flyers before her debut‚\nNo one took the flyers from a rookie‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なら、いっそここで歌おう！　って言って\n麻奈が歌ったら、あっという間に全部ハケました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so she said‚ \"Let's sing here!\"\nWhen Mana started singing‚ they were gone in no time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "……それが、伝説のアイドルの始まりだったと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…And that was the beginning of the legendary idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "全部って言っても、大した量じゃなかったですけどね\nでも……そうですね、あれが始まりだったかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it wasn't a large quantity‚ though.\nBut… yes‚ that might have been the start.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "って、いきなり昔話をしてすみません\n……ええと、franさん、今日はお洒落ですね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry for the sudden reminiscing.\nUm‚ fran-san‚ you're looking quite stylish today‚ aren't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "いつもと大して変わりませんよ\nいつもお洒落してるって言うなら、その通りですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not much different from usual.\nIf you say I'm always stylish‚ then yes‚ that's correct.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんこそ服をなんとかして下さい\n休日なのにスーツで出勤、お疲れ様ですこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you‚ {user}-san‚ should do something about your clothes.\nComing to work in a suit on a day off… that must be tiring.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "これは……その\nfranさんと私服で並ぶのは、どうも気後れしまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… um…\nI feel a bit intimidated standing next to you in casual wear‚ that's all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "あなたも一応、芸能界の人間なんですから\nちゃんとした服くらい持ってて下さいよ、本当に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're still in showbiz‚\nyou should have proper clothes seriously.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ忙しいところ、私のために出てきてもらったので\n今日はとやかくは言いませんけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won't fuss about it today\nsince you came out for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、行きましょうか\n案内、よろしくお願いしますね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shall we go then?\nPlease lead the way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3733.3333332999955,
          "startTime": 121.6333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.3833333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.3833333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん……ローカルな街歩き番組に出てきそうな\n風情ある商店街ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… It feels like a quaint shopping district\nthat could appear on a local city walking program.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "この先をしばらく歩いた所に公園がありまして\nそこで毎年、星見まつりというのをやってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just ahead‚ there's a park\nwhere they hold the Hoshimi Festival every year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "へえ、楽しそうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ sounds like fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "新人の頃、麻奈もそこでライブを開催したんですけど\nいきなり大雨になって、中止になりかけたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back when Mana was a rookie‚ she held a live performance there once.\nBut then‚ it suddenly started pouring rain‚ almost canceling the event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "でも麻奈がステージに立ったら、雨がぱーっと上がって\n星がよく見えて……あれは、本当に綺麗でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But as soon as Mana stepped onto the stage‚ the rain stopped‚\nand the stars were shining so brightly… It was really beautiful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "……なるほど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（あ、また俺ばっかり喋ってた）\n（麻奈に興味あるみたいだし、大丈夫……とは思うけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Oops‚ I'm talking too much again.）\n（It might be okay since she seems to be interested in Mana but…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "何か食べたい物があればご馳走しますよ\n……と言っても、そんな派手な物はないですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If there's anything you'd like to eat‚ I'll treat you.\n…It's not something flashy though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 177.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
