      "text": "そうですか？　なら、せっかくの機会ですし\nタカり……いえ、お言葉に甘えようかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so? Well‚ since it's a special occasion‚\nI owe you… Oh I meant I shall accept your kind offer",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 182.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
