      "text": "タカり……？　そういえばfranさんって\nお菓子とか食べてるところ、あまり見かけませんね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Owe me…? Oh‚ speaking of which‚ fran-san‚\nI don't see you eating sweets or snacks often.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshiarcade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 189.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "これでも食べる物には気を付けてるんです\nスタイルの維持も仕事のうちですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm careful about what I eat.\nMaintaining my body figure is part of the job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_03_02-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "小腹が空いた時にはナッツとかよく食べてますね\n低糖質で腹持ちもいいですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I often have nuts when I get hungry.\nThey're low in carbo and keep me full.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
